<paragraph id="8BE3860FFFE6FFEBFF76FEF1079DFE05" blockId="10.[168,778,160,599]" pageId="10" pageNumber="489">
<emphasis id="B9285A1DFFE6FFEBFF76FEF10466FECA" bold="true" box="[168,330,266,290]" pageId="10" pageNumber="489">Identification.</emphasis>
Plants pale green. Leaves alternate, distant to subimbricate, symmetrical, bifid 1/5‒1/4 lobe length, with a broad acuminate, rounded sinus, acuminate lobes, uniseriate tips 3‒6 cells long, margin entire; median cells isodiametric, thin walled, trigones small, cuticle smooth. Underleaves distant, 1‒2 × stem width, bifid near the base, with a short or long tooth on outer margin.
</paragraph>
